## Examples

Statement: "The keystore encrypts all secrets at rest using AES-256-GCM."
System Context: "hKask keystore implementation"
{"ontological_mode":"IS","epistemic_mode":"declarative","constraint_force":"Evidence","provenance":"implementation","confidence":0.95,"reasoning":"Descriptive claim about how the keystore works (IS). Asserted as verifiable fact (declarative). Maps to Evidence since it's an IS-Declarative statement. Provenance is implementation — from the code. High confidence because this is a concrete technical claim."}

